help.dmGeneral:
**Bot Alliance HQ** — use `/help` no servidor da aliança para passos conforme seu papel.

Comandos: `/link`, `/link-commander`, `/vr`, `/immunity`, `/thp`, `/what-is-my-vr`, `/what-is-my-vr-chart`, `/what-is-my-thp`, `/what-is-my-thp-chart`, `/who-is-conductor`, `/language`. Donos: `/link-alliance`. Oficiais (R4+): `/vr-report`, `/set-conductor`, `/train-is-ready`.

**Guia completo:** {guideUrl}

